{"tid":1283599,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共交通部：將麻六甲海峽安保提升至最高級","createTime":"2019-07-04T00:33:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T01:07:30.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b7f3fee835d7d8890e7d4f4368ce4cce21e754ec","tid":1283599,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T00:33:42.000Z","msg":"中共交通部：將麻六甲海峽安保提升至最高級<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7331/3907659\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7331%2F3907659&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O2%2FWCCUevL1oElw8znUqpaw%3D&h=0c8e0bc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7331/3907659</a><br />\n<br />\n7月3日，一份由中共交通運輸部辦公廳發布的「關於將航行於及擬駛往麻六甲海峽的中國籍國際航行船舶保安等級提升為3級的通知」在網路廣泛流傳。據悉，大陸多家船公司確認，的確收到該通知，並已採取相關應對措施。<br />\n<br />\n這份發給各國際航運公司、各直屬海事局的「交通運輸部辦公廳關於將航行於及擬駛往麻六甲海峽的中國籍國際航行船舶保安等級提高為3級的通知」稱，安保升級時間從2019年7月2日22時起，截止時間另行通知。"},{"pid":"42075b24264774efcd4bb4b27b52f1c33833186f","tid":1283599,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T00:34:05.000Z","msg":"根據多維網報導，中國國際船舶保安規則中的相關規定：傳播保安等級從低到高分為3級。保安等級1：是指應當始終保持的最低防範性保安措施的等級；保安等級2：是指由於保安事件危險性昇高而應在一段時間內保持適當的附加保護性保安措施的等級；保安等級3：是指當保安事件可能或者即將發生（儘管可能尚無法確定具體目標）時應在一段有限時間內保持進一步的特殊保護性保安措施的等級。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，本次通知中擬將船舶保安等級為3級，同時也是最高級，此前荷莫茲海峽油輪被襲擊後該地區的保安等級也才被定位2級，因此3級這個保安等級極為罕見。<br />\n<br />\n有大陸航運公司表示，這應該引起所有相關船舶、船東、以及海員的重視。<br />\n<br />\n馬六甲海峽是通往中國南海地區的交通要道，具有巨大的經濟、軍事意義。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，麻六甲海峽是世界上最繁忙的海峽之一，無論在經濟或軍事上，都是很重要的國際水道。經麻六甲海峽進入南海地區的油輪是經過蘇伊士運河的3倍、巴拿馬運河的5倍，中國大陸大部分的石油進口都要經過麻六甲海峽。<br />\n<br />\n今天正值中共南海軍演的最後一天，中共日前將南沙與中沙群島之間公海2.2萬平方公里劃為「禁航區」。"},{"pid":"e971d84d8a683dd70d1255fe858d1b92e7e45005","tid":1283599,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T00:51:58.000Z","msg":"純製造緊張等人唔好理香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9529bb70bf59d952c0cf7ba8eb65b7f51ac3d4b6","tid":1283599,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:00:29.000Z","msg":"理撚得佢"},{"pid":"2279adc5fcdd556474841b344fa693639bf7f9cf","tid":1283599,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:15:14.000Z","msg":"驚比人斷石油?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51ec27f4d31c8218680d45f1386bdae8320cd938","tid":1283599,"uid":134323,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:18:21.000Z","msg":"星加坡地頭到你話事咩"},{"pid":"dfc7f8257f04c1a25e2c9a2e55d13f143e84edc7","tid":1283599,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:10:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4417401e6d7675b775d78a2d6a229820e42bb28f","tid":1283599,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfc7f8257f04c1a25e2c9a2e55d13f143e84edc7","tid":1283599,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:10:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e7a7e9d8136aa52f825cdf856fc76899a2c858d","tid":1283599,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:12:02.000Z","msg":"麻乜六甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im